        "template--16695234232565__0bc84366-5786-499f-aa68-e76ccdeab634-1676539204e31e7f26-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With a rich heritage of almost two decades, Paez has carved a niche for itself in the world of casual footwear. But have you ever wondered how Paez Shoes go from a mere design to a finished product that finds its way to your feet? Now is your chance to take a deep dive into the intricate world of Paez's production process.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "template--16695234232565__0bc84366-5786-499f-aa68-e76ccdeab634-1676539204e31e7f26-1"
