    "ad910a1c-3462-4198-a45e-4b989f7be8ab": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "template--16695234232565__ad910a1c-3462-4198-a45e-4b989f7be8ab-1676539204e31e7f26-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Step 1",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "a5a39b4d-4306-4e20-af39-7a12c88ca7ec": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Design and Development",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "template--16695234232565__ad910a1c-3462-4198-a45e-4b989f7be8ab-1676539204e31e7f26-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Everything starts in Lisbon, Portugal. The production process begins in-house, with our creative director, Carolina Jarnac, who carefully crafts each and every design to meet the highest standards of quality and innovation, and brings to life new and trendy shoes.<br/><br/>\"The collection is all about good vibes and has the perfect mixture of maturity and fantasy, because Paez will always be fun and laid-back. We wanted to deliver shoes that are both versatile and stylish. By making sure that each design serves different purposes, we're living the motto \"Walk the Talk\" and ensuring that Paez can be a unique fashion statement. The collection is relaxed yet always cool, whether you're running errands, hitting the town, or simply lounging around.\"</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
