          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From there, our designs are sent to our trusted production partners at Lexelart (LXL) in Spain and Vietnam. LXL is specialized in the sustainable development of footwear, mainly focused on using responsible materials, and they carefully select suppliers based on their certification in using recycled materials.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
