            "text": "<p>Once the materials have been sourced, LXL brings the designs to life by developing the lasts, and patterns and creating vendor samples for review and approval by Paez.<br/><br/>Interested in more? <a href=\"https://paez.com/blogs/news/a-behind-the-scenes-look-at-the-paez-production-process-part-2\" title=\"https://paez.com/blogs/news/a-behind-the-scenes-look-at-the-paez-production-process-part-2\">Click this link</a> to find out more about Part 2 in our behind the scenes of the Paez production process!</p>",
